views.markdown: If you need help with "NewTerm (iOS 10 – 13)", you can contact HASHBANG Productions , the developer, via e-mail.
HASHBANG Productions  is the maintainer of the package "NewTerm (iOS 10 – 13)". Please contact them via email for any questions on this version of the package.
If you found a mistake in the depiction or cannot download the package, you can reach out to the maintainer of the "KT-Stations" repo, KT-Stations.
